text: Pankovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Dubrovskoye Rural Settlement, Yelovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 32 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 33 km WSW from Yelovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yelovsky District
title: Pankovo, Yelovsky District, Perm Krai
